premise_source_doc_sentence: The character of Lex Luthor , first created for comic books by Jerry Siegel and Joe Shuster in 1940 as nemesis of Superman , was adapted to television in 2001 by Alfred Gough and Miles Millar -- this is only the third time the character has been adapted to a live action television series .
